title: Product Requirements Document - IntentText Editor
summary: Requirements for a web-based IntentText editor with real-time collaboration

section: Overview
sub: Problem Statement
note: Current IntentText workflow requires CLI tools and manual file management. Users need a visual editor with real-time preview and collaboration features.

sub: Solution
- Web-based editor with live preview
- Real-time collaboration (like Google Docs)
- Visual block editor (Notion-style)
- Built-in query and validation

section: User Stories
sub: Writers
- As a writer, I want to see formatted preview while typing so I can verify formatting
- As a writer, I want to drag-and-drop blocks to reorganize content
- As a writer, I want templates for common document types

sub: Developers  
- As a developer, I want to query documents programmatically so I can build tools
- As a developer, I want schema validation to ensure document integrity
- As a developer, I want to embed IntentText in my applications

sub: Teams
- As a team member, I want to see who is editing in real-time
- As a team member, I want to comment on specific blocks
- As a team member, I want @mentions to notify colleagues

